jungle.toomany: A small spider monkey swoops out of the jungle and snatches it up. Climbing a tree too thin for you he sits, waves and chatters at you.
With a silent whooosh a gorilla swings by on a vine and snatches it right out of your hand, almost dislocating your shoulder.
A big gorilla knocks you down and grabs it! Before you can collect your wits he vanishes as quickly as he came taking your item with him.
A chimpanzee darts out of the brush, steals it and then disappears into the thick plant life.
An entire family of big gorillas pounce from out of the brush knock you down, scoop everything up but your bag and run away!
